      "raw_text": "N. 8. Twitchnal and N. II. Twitch-\nnal, brothers. who give their resi-\ndence as Mission. Chelan county. filed\npetitions in bankruptcy in the United\nStates court this morning. They give\ntheir occupation as farmers.\n\n\nTheir liabilities are $2417.21 each.\nOne claims to have no assets. while\nthe other has assets amounting to\n$3.50, which consists Of section of\nland too dry and sterile to produce\ncrops until provided with water for\nirrigation."
